EFL Edje Theme Editor
*********************

Requirements
============

Must have:
 Elementary (1.7.8) with deps
 Autotools
 check (optional)

Compiling and installing
========================

1) Install EFL libraries (http://www.enlightenment.org/p.php?p=download).
2) Install Autotools.
3) Build eflete from top source directory.

Build
=====

   mkdir build
   cd build
   autoreconf -f -i ..
   ../configure
   make && sudo make install

To install program to specified directory use --prefix option on configure step:

   ../configure --prefix=/full/path/to/some/dir

Run tests
=========

   make check

Run editor
==========

   eflete

External resources used
=======================

FreeFont Mono from http://www.gnu.org/software/freefont/ (GNU GPL v.3)
